name: NOMEEE
description:
Nomeee is a new hybrid creature from an unexpected place between the present and future. It has arrived on Earth from a future gaze of posthumanism to reveal layers of humanity while challenging humans with difficult questions full of truths, lies, and half-truths.  Maybe it can help us understand new perspectives of what it means to be human while we try and understand what Nomeee is, and how it reflects on humanity from an unknown future.
